## Version bumps (semver)

| Part | When |
|------|------|
| **PATCH** `x.x.X` | Fixes, copy, small UI |
| **MINOR** `x.X.0` | New behavior, larger UI |
| **MAJOR** `X.0.0` | Breaking / architecture |

