## Checklist (agents)

1. `HMO_VERSION` + header match in `hostlinks-marketing-ops.php`
2. `readme.txt` changelog (if you ship user-visible changes)
3. PowerShell: `git add -A` ŌåÆ `commit` ŌåÆ **`push origin main`**
4. Confirm Actions release job and zip on GitHub
